extendedInfo.description: Boat Ramps from TakeMeFishing.org is an exciting new app that lets you quickly locate and get directions to more than 35,000 boat ramps throughout the U.S. Boat Ramps from TakeMeFishing.org has an easy-to-use interface and provides a list of ramps close to your current location or any address, zip code or city you enter into the application. Once youâve found the boat ramp youâre looking for, the app can even provide you with directions to the ramp.

reviews.title: Too much noise
reviews.comment: There isn\'t a search option, so you have to look by map. All the pins look the same, and when you find a ramp, no information.
reviews.author: Les Stockett

reviews.title: Nice
reviews.comment: I live between 2 rivers with many local lakes with ramps also. Very handy app.
